Class MinimalFeatureEvidenceUpdater

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.impl.minimal.MinimalFeatureEnricher<FeatureEvidence>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.impl.minimal.MinimalFeatureEvidenceEnricher

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, FeatureEnricher<FeatureEvidence>, EnricherListener<Protein>, InteractorEnricherListener<Protein>, ProteinEnricherListener, MIEnricher<FeatureEvidence>, ProteinListeningFeatureEnricher<FeatureEvidence>, AliasesChangeListener<Protein>, AnnotationsChangeListener<Protein>, ChecksumsChangeListener<Protein>, IdentifiersChangeListener<Protein>, InteractorChangeListener<Protein>, PolymerChangeListener<Protein>, ProteinChangeListener, XrefsChangeListener<Protein>
    public class MinimalFeatureEvidenceUpdater
extends MinimalFeatureEvidenceEnricher
    Provides minimal update of feature evidence. - update minimal properties of feature. See MinimalFeatureUpdater - update detection methods if cv term enricher is not null - Ignore all other properties of a feature
    Since:
    13/08/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
